data.description: Discover this flawlessly renovated two-story home, ideally located for convenience! Unwind on the expansive covered front porch with a freshly brewed cup of coffee. Step inside to find updated LVP throughout the spacious living room with decorative fireplace, leading seamlessly to an open-concept dining area and modernized kitchen. Ascend the stairs to three generously proportioned bedrooms, accompanied by a revamped full bath. Descend from the main living space to a full, unfinished basement, offering abundant storage and laundry capabilities. The backyard beckons for gardening endeavors, socializing around a fire pit, and provides ample off-street parking. Move in with peace of mind, knowing the roof, siding, and mechanical systems are all brand new!
